sentences: Rola Youssef Saad (Arabic: رولا يوسف سعد; born 25 August 1978) is a Lebanese pop singer and model who emerged in the mid-2000s and is most commonly known for her collaboration with Lebanese singer Sabah.
Rola Saad was born in Beirut, Lebanon, to a Christian Maronite family (originally from Tannourine)
Rola Saad is now married and living in Beirut.
